# ============================================================
# .gitignore — ARGUS
# Adaptive Reconnaissance and Gaze Understanding System
#
# Polyglot research repo: Python (primary) + ML/CV artifacts,
# optional native C/C++/CUDA extensions, and a JS/TS dashboard.
# Large data (recordings, frames, weights) is managed out-of-band
# (DVC / git-LFS / object storage), never committed to git.
# Keep-exceptions for sample data and fixtures live at the bottom.
# ============================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Secrets & environment
# Never commit real credentials. Keep a committed *.example template.
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.envrc
.direnv/
secrets.yaml
secrets.yml
credentials.json
*.pem
id_rsa
id_dsa
id_ecdsa
id_ed25519
*_rsa
*_ed25519
*_ecdsa
.aws/
gha-creds-*.json

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Python
# ------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

